title: RioRand Pink Professional & Fast Nail Art Drill Electric File Acrylics Salon Equipment
description: This is the fastest in the industry and great for all types of nail work, from sculpting, buffing, to polishing.It features a professional foot pedal control and digital power supply source for a steady, precise speed setting.Your new drill comes with everything you need to get started and more!Note: Pls kindly be noted the 2nd picture"how to insert the bit".Operation Detail:* plug in the electric cord of the transformer to the main electric outlet* turn on the on/off switch on the transformer.(machine should be at the lowest speed when turning on)* select the desired speed by turning the variable speed control knob on the transformer* The black switch in front of the transformer, next to the speed control selection knob is for forward and reverse rotation direction* To use the foot pedal control,connect the end of the cord from the foot pedel to the out put hole at the front of the transformer and press down on the foot pedal*To secure the bits:A.Turn the pink rubber sleeve to the R side's end.  B.Push in the desired bit firmly into the hole.  C.Turn the pink rubber sleeve to the S side's to close.* To remove the bits: turn off the machine,twist the pink rubber sleeve to the S side's end to open the chuck,then plug off it.Safety rules:* Always unplug the tool when you change accessory or collect* Do not engage the shaft lock button while the tool is running* Do not use near or place in water.if motor falls into water, unplug immediately.* Do not touch the bit after use. The bit is too hot to be touched by bare hands* Keep dust out of eyes and lungs by using protective eyewear or a dust mask*Turn speed control to minimum before turning off and switch the main power source to 0.* Always unplug it and clear the dust after use* When the machine is not in use, all tool must be stored in a dry location abd keep out of reach of children.
